      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. This high-revving straight-six features a 3.2L displacement with individual throttle bodies and a responsive Double VANOS variable valve timing system. The power is delivered through a tactile six-speed manual transmission to a rear-mounted limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid, with critical subframe reinforcement already addressed, ensuring predictable turn-in and cornering stability. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with exceptional thermal efficiency. A true driver\u2019s car optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
